The paper deals with detecting fake views in online video services, which involves analyzing large amounts of data and detecting patterns. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), or Security and Cryptography (cs.CR) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of algorithms to detect fake views in real-time, which could fall under the Streaming and Online Algorithms (cs.SI) sub-category. Finally, the paper also involves analyzing and processing large amounts of data, which could fall under the Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-category.
